txt.en: Your efforts have lessened the amount of Warg-riders in Târ-kútoz, and for that, the dwarves at Ashmargathâl are grateful.
Goblins riding fierce Wargs pose a threat to the Haban'akkâ, especially in the mountains where footing is treacherous. Defeating Warg-riders in Târ-kútoz will help the dwarves at Ashmargathâl.
Moria Warg-riders can be found roaming around Târ-kútoz.\n\nDefeating these Warg-riders will help the dwarves at Ashmargathâl.
